<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Sazuk nih rial ti dai, a ngaih bantuk in
 Maw Pathian kan ngai, Nangmah lawng
 Biak kan duh, Kan bochan Bawipa ka
 Thinlung tak in

[C1]
   Nangmah lawng ka tthawnnak kan phaw
   Ka thlarau nih nangmah chung lawngah
   Nangmah lawng biak kan duh
   Kan bochan Bawipa ka, thinlung tak in.

[V2]
 Siangpahrang si hmanh law, Ka Unau le
 Ka hawi thabik na si, Kan dawt ko zeizong
 Vial-te nak in kan dawt deuh, Jesuh ka Bawi.

[V3]
 Sui le ngun nakin kan, tleihchan Bawipa
 Hnangam tertu na si, Nangmah lawng
 Kei ca lawmh-nak pe khotu Pathian, Bawibik na si.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>SAZUK BANG</title>
</song>